Package: nn2poly.tools
Title: Auxiliar package to the `nn2poly` package. Implements custom layers using `keras`and `tensorflow`that impose the needed restrictions in the weight norms to ensure a good performance of the NN2Poly method. 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
